{"id":"bruit","term":"Bruit","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>A rumour or report (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Jeremiah 10:22\">Jer. 10:22</a>, R.V. “rumour;” <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nahum 3:19\">Nah. 3:19</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Jeremiah 10:22","Nahum 3:19"]}